Code availability All the codes used in this work are based on standard, publicly available software packages, as detailed in the Methods section. The software used for Molecular Dynamics simulations is LAMMPS, version 30july2016, and HOOMD, version 2.9.x. 3D structures visualization was realized with the POV-Ray software, version 3.7. All the codes required to perform the simulations of the polymer models are provided at https://github.com/ ehsanirani/PhaseSeparation-LoopExtrusion-MD87.

